  <div class="page-mission">
    <p>Getting to know someone or something is an exciting experience - a journey.</p>
    <p>End every journey starts with a first step.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Journey: First Step -->
<section id="journey-first-step" class="content-section padding-section-y">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>Our first step</h2>
      <hr>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="content-box about-me">
        <div class="text">
          <h4>The Travel destination of this journey</h3>
          <p>This challenhge is a great opportunity to not only learn more about Accenture -
          but also to show my understanding of the you and that I would be a great fit.
          </p>
          <p>So accordingly, we are going to start by me making the first step and elaborating on my key traits. Next, we will see if you are as convinced as I am that we are a great fit!</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- Trait 01 -->
      <div class="content-box traits">
        <div class="card-traits">
          <div class="icon">01</div>
          <div class="content">
            <h3>Eagerness to learn</h3>
            <p>
              As a person, I love learning. It does not matter if it is a new skill, a (coding) langue, or the occational life lesson... I love the experience and learn new things.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Trait 2 -->
        <div class="card-traits">
          <div class="icon">02</div>
          <div class="content">
            <h3>Ability to adapt</h3>
            <p>
              In order to grow and make today even just a little bit better than yesterday, I will adapt. I will adapt to close the gaps in my knowledge and skill set and be as rigourous as possible to find those gaps in the first place.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Trait 3 -->
        <div class="card-traits">
          <div class="icon">03</div>
          <div class="content">
            <h3>Curious to see</h3>
            <p>
              Curiousity might have killed the cat. But, in secret, I have always been more of a dog person. I cannot help but wonder how, why, and where.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Journey: Second Step -->
<section id="journey-third-step" class="content-section padding-section-y">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
